# Business Requirements Document (BRD)

## Functional Requirements  
1. Implement structured onboarding paired with mentorship for new employees.  
2. Develop regular employee engagement programs and feedback channels.  
3. Establish clear career development pathways with training opportunities.  
4. Enhance attrition data analysis capabilities to monitor trends and predict risk.  
5. Maintain transparent internal communication on retention initiatives.

## Non-functional Requirements  
- Programs and tools should be accessible to all employees.  
- Data privacy must be maintained in all employee feedback systems.

## Constraints  
- Limited budget for new programs and analytics tools.  
- Existing HR systems have restricted data capabilities.
